# Android Reversing CTF Cheat Sheet

## 0. First Commands

```bash
file app.apk
unzip -l app.apk | less
apktool d app.apk -o apk_out
jadx-gui app.apk
```

Look for:

```text
flag
CTF
password
secret
check
verify
native
JNI
```

---

## 1. Main Tools

```bash
jadx-gui app.apk          # Java/Kotlin decompile
apktool d app.apk         # resources + smali
adb install app.apk       # install app
adb logcat                # logs
frida                    # runtime hook
objection                # easier Frida
ghidra                   # native .so analysis
```

---

## 2. APK Structure

```text
AndroidManifest.xml       # activities, permissions
classes.dex               # app code
resources.arsc            # resources
res/                      # strings/layouts
assets/                   # hidden files
lib/arm64-v8a/*.so        # native libraries
META-INF/                 # signing info
```

---

## 3. Manifest Recon

```bash
aapt dump badging app.apk
aapt dump xmltree app.apk AndroidManifest.xml
```

Check:

```text
package name
main activity
exported activities
permissions
deep links
debuggable=true
```

