## 4. Search Everything

```bash
grep -Rni "flag\|ctf\|secret\|password\|key\|check\|verify" apk_out/
```

In JADX search for:

```text
flag
checkFlag
verify
validate
success
wrong
Base64
AES
Cipher
MessageDigest
native
System.loadLibrary
```

