## 5. Java/Kotlin Easy Wins

Look for:

```java
if (input.equals("secret"))
```

or:

```java
String flag = "CTF{...}";
```

Also check:

```java
getString(R.string.secret)
```

Then open:

```text
res/values/strings.xml
```

