## 6. Base64 / Hex / ROT

Common patterns:

```java
Base64.decode(...)
Integer.parseInt(hex, 16)
StringBuilder.reverse()
```

Python decode:

```python
import base64
print(base64.b64decode("..."))
print(bytes.fromhex("..."))
```

---

## 7. Crypto Checks

Search:

```text
Cipher.getInstance
AES
DES
RC4
MessageDigest
SHA-256
MD5
SecretKeySpec
IvParameterSpec
```

Find:

```text
key
iv
ciphertext
salt
```

Common solve:

```python
from Crypto.Cipher import AES
from Crypto.Util.Padding import unpad

key = b"..."
iv = b"..."
ct = bytes.fromhex("...")

print(unpad(AES.new(key, AES.MODE_CBC, iv).decrypt(ct), 16))
```

