## 10. Smali Patching

Decode:

```bash
apktool d app.apk -o apk_out
```

Find wrong check:

```smali
if-eqz v0, :wrong
```

Patch to success:

```smali
goto :success
```

Rebuild:

```bash
apktool b apk_out -o patched.apk
```

Sign:

```bash
keytool -genkey -v -keystore ctf.keystore -alias ctf -keyalg RSA -keysize 2048 -validity 10000
apksigner sign --ks ctf.keystore patched.apk
```

Install:

```bash
adb install -r patched.apk
```

---

## 11. Native Library Detection

Search:

```java
System.loadLibrary("native-lib")
native boolean checkFlag(String s);
```

Then inspect:

```bash
find apk_out/lib -type f
file apk_out/lib/*/*
strings apk_out/lib/*/*
```

Open `.so` in Ghidra.

Look for:

```text
JNI_OnLoad
Java_com_package_Class_function
strcmp
memcmp
strlen
```

---

## 12. Native Function Names

JNI pattern:

```text
Java_com_example_app_MainActivity_checkFlag
```

If stripped, search strings and xrefs.

Useful:

```bash
nm -D libnative.so
readelf -s libnative.so
objdump -T libnative.so
```

