## 14. Frida Basics

Start app:

```bash
frida -U -f com.package.name
```

Hook Java method:

```js
Java.perform(function () {
  var Main = Java.use("com.example.MainActivity");

  Main.checkFlag.implementation = function (s) {
    console.log("input = " + s);
    var r = this.checkFlag(s);
    console.log("result = " + r);
    return true;
  };
});
```

Run:

```bash
frida -U -f com.package.name -l hook.js
```

---

## 15. Hook Return Value

Force success:

```js
Java.perform(function () {
  var Main = Java.use("com.example.MainActivity");

  Main.checkFlag.implementation = function (s) {
    return true;
  };
});
```

