## 27. Common Android CTF Patterns

| Pattern            | What to do                    |
| ------------------ | ----------------------------- |
| Hardcoded flag     | Search strings/resources      |
| Java checkFlag     | Read JADX                     |
| Smali condition    | Patch branch                  |
| Native JNI check   | Open `.so` in Ghidra          |
| AES encrypted flag | Recover key/IV/ciphertext     |
| Base64 flag        | Decode                        |
| Root check         | Patch/hook                    |
| Exported activity  | Start with adb                |
| Hidden asset       | Check assets/res/raw          |
| Flutter            | Inspect libapp.so             |
| Unity              | Decompile Assembly-CSharp.dll |

